{
  "texts": [
    "Guellil et al. [2021] propose 'one' model for sentiment classification in different dialects of Arabic.",
    "They use transliteration to map dialects to Standard Arabic.",
    "The sentiment analysis model itself uses word2vec features with statistical classifier.",
    "Finally, Husain et al. [2022] present statistical models based on SVM along with Transformers-based models like BERT.",
    "5.2.3 Incorporating dialect information in sentiment prediction."
  ]
}